{
  "document_id": "job-33",
  "title": "Job 33",
  "type": "scripture",
  "translation": "NRSVue",
  "blocks": [
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-1",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 1,
      "text": "“But now, hear my speech, O Job,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-2",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 2,
      "text": "See, I open my mouth;"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-3",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 3,
      "text": "My words declare the uprightness of my heart,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-4",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 4,
      "text": "The spirit of God has made me,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-5",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 5,
      "text": "Answer me, if you can;"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-6",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 6,
      "text": "See, before God I am as you are;"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-7",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 7,
      "text": "No fear of me need terrify you;"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-8",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 8,
      "text": "“Surely, you have spoken in my hearing,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-9",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 9,
      "text": "You say, ‘I am clean, without transgression;"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-10",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 10,
      "text": "Look, he finds occasions against me;"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-11",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 11,
      "text": "he puts my feet in the stocks"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-12",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 12,
      "text": "“But in this you are not right. I will answer you:"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-13",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 13,
      "text": "Why do you contend against him,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-14",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 14,
      "text": "For God speaks in one way"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-15",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 15,
      "text": "In a dream, in a vision of the night,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-16",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 16,
      "text": "then he opens their ears"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-17",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 17,
      "text": "that he may turn them aside from their deeds"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-18",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 18,
      "text": "to spare their souls from the Pit,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-19",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 19,
      "text": "They are also chastened with pain upon their beds"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-20",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 20,
      "text": "so that their lives loathe bread"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-21",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 21,
      "text": "Their flesh is so wasted away that it cannot be seen,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-22",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 22,
      "text": "Their souls draw near the Pit"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-23",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 23,
      "text": "Then, if there should be for one of them an angel,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-24",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 24,
      "text": "and he is gracious to that person and says,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-25",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 25,
      "text": "let his flesh become fresh with youth;"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-26",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 26,
      "text": "then he prays to God and is accepted by him;"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-27",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 27,
      "text": "That person sings to others and says,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-28",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 28,
      "text": "He has redeemed my soul from going down to the Pit,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-29",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 29,
      "text": "“God indeed does all these things,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-30",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 30,
      "text": "to bring back their souls from the Pit,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-31",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 31,
      "text": "Pay heed, Job, listen to me;"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-32",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 32,
      "text": "If you have anything to say, answer me;"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "job-33-33",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 33,
      "text": "If not, listen to me;"
    }
  ]
}